page.title: 12Schoolchild's day
page.content: MONDAY 7.20 AM gets up, 7.30 makes breakfast 8.10 catches school bus, 8.40 arrives at school, 8.55 goes into assembly, 9.20 History period, 10.10 English period, 10.15 interval, 11.30 Music period, 12.35 PM Lunch, 1.35 P.E. 2.40 Maths, 3.45 catches school bus, 4.20 gets home, changes and does homework, 4.50 watches television, 5.30 Dad arrives home and we have supper, 5.55 go to Guides, 6.00 Guides start, 7.30 Guides finish, 7.35 get home, 7.40 practice piano and clarinet, 8.40 tidy bedroom or watch T.V., 9.30 go to bed.
